:: Armoury {"position":"875,550","size":"100,100"}
<div style="font-size: 30px; text-align: center">
Pietro finds himself in the armoury of his master, the knight Annibale II Bentivoglio. By the light of the burning torch Pietro is holding, he can see a relatively small room with various armour hanging on the walls. In the corner of the room there is a couch, from which an elderly guard rises and adresses Pietro.

**Guard:** Are you from sir Bentivoglio?

**Pietro:** Yes, I am his new squire. For today's tournament, I have been tasked with selecting equipment for my lord.

**Guard:** All right, if I am not mistaken, today is a special day for you, when the fate of your future service will be decided. Well, so be it... Since you're new to this, I'll tell you what's here.
